## 11. File Deployment Discipline

- When downloading multiple files with the same name, macOS appends (1)/(2) suffixes. Always verify with `head -5` before placing.
- After `cp` to the Edge Functions directory, verify the file content before deploying.
- The Supabase secrets dashboard shows only digests, not raw values. The raw API_KEY_HMAC_SECRET must be preserved externally.

---

## 12. Checklist for New RPC Functions

Every new SECURITY DEFINER RPC must:

- [ ] Include `PERFORM set_config('app.tenant_id', p_tenant_id::text, true)`
- [ ] Include `WHERE tenant_id = p_tenant_id` on every query (never rely on RLS inside SECURITY DEFINER)
- [ ] Verify any referenced entity belongs to the tenant before operating on it
- [ ] Return only the columns needed (no SELECT *)

---

## 13. Checklist for New Tables

Every new tenant-scoped table must have:

- [ ] `tenant_id uuid NOT NULL REFERENCES tenants(id)` column
- [ ] RLS enabled with appropriate policies
- [ ] Subscription check trigger (`check_subscription_active`)
- [ ] If immutable: BEFORE UPDATE OR DELETE trigger
- [ ] Appropriate indexes (at minimum on tenant_id)

